            Advanced enterprise features for teams managing large conversation datasets.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Private team dashboards with role-based access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Call snippet bookmarking and sharing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>CRM integrations (HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Advanced search and filtering capabilities</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- v1.4 - AI Sales Agent -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl mr-3">ü§ñ</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">AI Sales Agent</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200 mt-1">
